thread.title: David Heritage
thread.title_full: Kezie.co.uk- http://www.kezie.co.uk/ reviewed by David Heritage

author: David Heritage
title: David Heritage
text: Ordered diced Kangaroo (our dog needs to be on a special diet for 8 weeks!). Great service starting with a phone call for advice. Delivery was perfect - arrived as described on the website - still frozen solid (we live in the far west of Cornwall so that was some journey). Pinched some of the kangaroo from our dog - delicious! - and will be trying some other products for ourselves.
